# Lambdapi compiled artifacts
**/*.lpo

# Python bytecode
**/__pycache__/

# status.py regression-floor cache (per-working-tree; the loop (re)saves it at
# session start and after each commit — not a shared/committed artifact)
tools/port_baseline.json

# Isabelle backups
**/*.thy~

# Editor / OS noise
*~
.DS_Store
\#*\#
.#*

# Claude Code per-user local settings (hook script under .claude/hooks/ is shared)
.claude/settings.local.json

# Documentation lives in README.md only. Ignore stray/scratch .md (review notes,
# generated reports such as FAITHFULNESS.md). Already-tracked docs (CLAUDE.md,
# isabelle-src/README.md) stay tracked and committable — .gitignore does not
# untrack files, it only stops new ones from being added.
*.md
!README.md
!PORTING_LOOP.md

# Agent worktrees
.claude/worktrees/
